            "content_html": "<p>  为防止以后找不到，💻备份一下两款小米📱专用刷机工具<mark>闪米</mark><sup>(miflash)</sup><br>\n1・miflash_pro   刷机工具更多，更全面。<br>\n2・MiFlash2020   单独的<mark> FASTBOOT 模式</mark>线刷工具<br>\n<img data-src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2023/02/10/bEaimsOcB7yduN3.png\" alt=\"MiFlash.png\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"miflash_pro-7370621\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#miflash_pro-7370621\">#</a> miflash_pro-7.3.706.21</h4>\n<p>百度盘永久链接：<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9wYW4uYmFpZHUuY29tL3MvMU1vdi1aVnNsc21OMW9uN1FSRnI5OVE/cHdkPXlqazE=\">https://pan.baidu.com/s/1Mov-ZVslsmN1on7QRFr99Q?pwd=yjk1</span><br>\n 提取码：yjk1<br>\n 第三方网站链接：<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9taXVpdmVyLmNvbS9taWZsYXNoLXByby8=\">https://miuiver.com/miflash-pro/</span><br>\n 下载可能更快一些，就是不知道网站存在多久，推荐各位养成自己备份的好习惯。</p>\n<h4 id=\"miflash2020-3-14-0\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#miflash2020-3-14-0\">#</a> MiFlash2020-3-14-0</h4>\n<p>链接：<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9wYW4uYmFpZHUuY29tL3MvMW9MTUhfNnU3MmJkSFJxZmRLN2JIQWc/cHdkPWdwYWU=\">https://pan.baidu.com/s/1oLMH_6u72bdHRqfdK7bHAg?pwd=gpae</span><br>\n 提取码：gpae<br>\n 第三方：<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9taXVpdmVyLmNvbS9taWZsYXNoLw==\">https://miuiver.com/miflash/</span></p>\n<h4 id=\"申请解锁小米手机\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#申请解锁小米手机\">#</a> 申请解锁小米手机</h4>\n<p>小米官方解锁申请：<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubWl1aS5jb20vdW5sb2NrL2luZGV4Lmh0bWw=\">https://www.miui.com/unlock/index.html</span><br>\n⚠️<br>\n  就第一个下载快一点，还是推荐各位使用专用下载工具辅助解析下载。</p>\n",
